Content: Pro traders arent any better at predicting where the market will go than a hobby trader and its not the job. The difference is all in execution Finding lvls protecting profits once available stopping out  adjusting when wrong and consistant loss size control. Focus there

5585 to 5664 remains the 2 week range in #ES_F  5630 failure triggered down to range support as posted. We are now probing below the range for the 3rd time in last 2 weeks last two were traps as are 90. 5598 must reclaim to trigger back up the range.  5572 5562 next supports

We continue to fill out the 56595588 chop zone in #ES_F and as posted we are building structure to setup the next trend leg do not overtrade in it. 5642 and 5630 were todays pivots  after bouncing twice 30 flushed  5630 must reclaim now to pop to 5642. 5612 5605 are below

Closing update #ES_F Nice bounce on the reclaim of 5788 but ultimately stuck in the no volatility 582330 to 5772 chop range. We hit restarget this morning now dipped to supports. 5788 5773 must hold for bulls. Newsletter out soon talking triggers tradecompanion.substack.com

Closing update Volatility finally returns in ES. I wrote that 5773 must reclaim to resume up back to 5795 and we are here now as #ES_F put in a failed breakdown. Lock in gains here. 5810 5828 next. Sell again5773. newsletter out soon talking triggers tradecompanion.substack.com

Price continues to be stuck on repeat in #ES_F as we fill out the 5585 to 5662 two week range. 563025 failure triggered down as posted to 558590 range support and we are still here after the standard quick trap below.  5598 next up must recover to work back up the range again

5773 remains the most important level in #ES_F. I was support this morning with 5795 target. It held exact ran there. 1 hour ago it failed and we got 15 point flush but bears dropped the ball  it reclaimed.  No change 73 must hold to keep 95 live. It fails we sell again

As warned hourly since 830AM 5773 was the key support in #ES_F and this mornings bounce was likely to be its last. We held it bounced to 5795 target then lost to trigger short  5763 5751 were sell targets and we just hit 63. 51 next then 40. 5773 must reclaim to resume up

It took all day but theres finally a support test in #ES_F. 582330 to 5773 is the range with 5788 key pivot in between. We ran to 5823 target this morning putting 5788 in play. This is a weak well tested level.   Bulls cant hold we test 5772 final support before sell

And theres the full range round trip in #ES_F and this should not be surprising to anyone by now. 5664 to 558590 has been the multiweek range. 562530 fail triggered down to 5611 558590 and we are here again.  558590support. Bulls need fast reaction here or 5566 next down

We continue to traverse the 56645585 range as we have now for 2 weeks in #ES_F. On the 31st test 562530 cracked again. 5611 5598 were supports below as posted  pushing to 5598 now. Below there is 558590 which is range support and must hold  562630 reclaim triggers squeeze

Its been 2 full weeks now in the 56645585 range in #ES_F with 562530 middle magnettrap zone and we are now on the 31st test of this level. This range will continue to eat up overtraders and those not trading the traps.  Bulls must recover 5630 to pop. 56115598 are below

Todays targets were 5788 then 5795 in #ES_F off the 5773 major support and bullbear line. We held 5773 exact this morning ran to 5795 where I warned to lock in gains then dipped   5773 incoming again big decision point incoming. Fails we start the leg down 5763 5751.

Today two targets were provided in #ES_F 5788 then 5795 hit. These were off 5773 key support which held nicely possibly for the last time though. Protect those profits Powell speaks in 30mins.  Bulls must hold 577375 to keep 5810 5823 live. 73 fails sell 5763 5751

Its been good but very slow follow through on this sell in #ES_F as we fill out that 582330 to 5773 range. We popped to 5823 target this morning  now filling range to the downside  No change 5788 close now this is weak 5773 must hold to keep bulls in control. Short73

On Thursday at 4pm longs triggered at 558893 with 565359 target. #ES_F testedprobed above that res 5x. This entire range 5659 to 5588 is the new chop zone zone to setup what should be a large trend leg  No change. 5642 must recover to resume up. 5612 5605 next supports

Snails pace action continues in #ES_F as warned dont overtrade. We need volatility to trade. 582330 to 5772the chop range. Todays targets were 5810 5823 5830 and we popped to 5823 and dipped.  Now bulls must hold 5788 5773 on this dip to retain control and see new highs

Dip underway for #ES_F as 5653 remains a brick wall resistance with 5 tests and two probes above. I posted 5642 was support weaker now and after defending overnight it flushed. 5630 was below as posted hit.  5642 must recover now to resume up. 5630 fails we see 5612 next

After the Thursday 5588 long trigger 5653 was the target  it now has 5 tests including two probes above. Magnet. It remains the gate to higher prices likely ATHs when #ES_F is ready.  No change. 5642support weaker now. Must hold to keep 75 8790 live. Sell to 5630 below

For 2 weeks #ES_F has been in the 55855664 range with a 5630 magnet. After hitting 5662 target yesterday we just hit the 5630 for the 30th test since Aug19 a likely record  Plan today 562530support. Weak. Bulls cant push fast here 5648 5664 res sell 5610 5598

Since the 5588 long trigger on Thursday at 4pm 5653 was my target in #ES_F for Friday. Weve now tested it 4x  are basing above. No change just keep holding those runners this zone is the gate to higher.  5672 568790 next up when ES ready. 5642support weak now.Dip below

Ultra low volatility continues as we fill out the 5773 to 5830 chop range in #ES_F. Today targets were 5810 hit 5823 hit 5830 and we got to 5823 and dipped  No change and 5788 5773 lowest must hold on this which keeps bulls in firm control for new highs. 5773 failsshort

5795 target #2 hit in #ES_F. As posted this morning all that matters is 5773. It held this morning may be the last time. Targets were 5788 hit 5795 hit. Its all just bonus now hold runners and wait for volatility to spike. 5810 5823 next  up.  Sell  5773 to 5763 5751

Low volatility continues in #ES_F. I provided 3 targets for today. 5810 hit 5823 1 point shy 5830 breakout. We are basing 5830 to 5773 do not overtrade when volatility just isnt there  No change 5788 weak 5772 must hold to keep bulls in full control. Sell under

5810 was todays 1st target and we hit in #ES_F. It then became support. 5823 is target #2 and we are pushing there slowly then 5830 breakout. We remain in a very low volatility regime dont overtrade. 58305773a chop playground.  Bulls must hold 5788 5773 to retain control

5773 remains all that matters in #ES_F 57735823chop. We tested 5773 this morning held exact. 5782 reclaim was needed to trigger long to 5788 5795 and we are at 5788 for 1hr.  Protect those profits leave runner. 5795 5810 if bulls want it. 5773 fails we sell 5763 5751

Good level to level pop in #ES_F. 5773 remains key must hold support. We held 5773 exact reclaimed 5782 to trigger up  as posted then hit 5788 1st target. Protect those profits if long 5773 remains weak and well tested.  5795 5810 if ES wants. 5773 fails sell 5763 5751

We continue to build structure to setup the next trend leg in #ES_F. Dont overtrade. 5642 and 5630 were key pivots today as posted. We held 5642 overnight sold down to 5630 this morning now back at 5642.   56595588chop range sets up 568790 when ES is ready. Sell5630

On ThursdayFriday my target off 558893 buy zone was 5653  #ES_F certainly agrees testing it 4x just since Friday morning.  Plan today No change keep holding runners from Fri. 5642 held 2x weaksupport. Basing above keeps 5672 568790 live direct. 5642 fails sell 5630

5810 1st target up for today tagged in #ES_F and we remain in a low volatility regime dont overtrade. Generally 58305773 is a broad chop range with 5788 being a key midpivot.  5810 now support 5823 5830 breakout if ES wants. 5788 5773 must hold on dips or we collapse

As discussed at length for a week 5773 is key and #ES_F agrees holding it precisely. 5773 to 582330the multi week range. This may be the last chance bulls get off 5773 very weak so they have to make it work.  5782 must recover to see 88 95. 5773 fails sell 5764 5751

As posted Friday last week #ES_F was in a chop range 582330 to 5773. Friday I was looking for a rally to resistance  we hit it. Now were at support and its weakwell tested  Plan today Bulls must react fastrecover 5783 for 1 last rally shot. 5773 fails sell 5763 5751

Yesterday was all about 1 level in #ES_F 5790. After breaking it out we ran to 5823 target and 5790 became support. Weve tested it 3x with one actionable failed breakdown 1pm ystd  Plan today 5788 well tested 5772supports. Keeps 5810 5823 5830 live. Short only5772

CLosing update 559388 major support as posted and #ES_F agrees basing here for 2hrs now bulls want to hold this. All comes down to Jackson Hole tmrw. 5578 554346 if it cracks overnight. Newsletter out soon talking my planentries from here tradecompanion.substack.com

Levels respecting precisely today in #ES_F. 559388 was sell target as posted and weve hit it and now spent 1.5hrs bouncing here. This is a big inflection zone. Bulls will need to recover 561520 now to set a more sustained low.  559388 fails we take another leg down to 5543

Its the best session volatility wise since #ES_F bottomed 11 days ago but the real moves come tomorrow. Levels respecting precisely 559388 was sell target as posted and we hit exact and bounced.  Bulls need to push fast here. 5578 5543 below. 561520 must reclaim to rally

Bidirectional price action is back in #ES_F at least for the day after 11 days of grind up. After tagging 5662 resistance I posted 561520 had to reclaim to rally. It did and we got to 5630 then sold.  Same drill now 561520 must reclaim to trigger up 559388next support.

Price finally woke up from its low volatility grind in #ES_F and presenting good twoway setups. 5662 was target #1 this morning. We sold off there. I posted 561520 had to reclaim to rally we reclaimed and 15 points  No change 5643 5652 5662 next above. 561520support

Price #ES_F is waking up slightly from its 11 day low volatility grind up mode good to see but all noise until Jackson Hole tomorrow at 10am. It began after tagging 5662 1st target today which was July 18th peak.  558894 next support down 561520 must reclaim to rally

A rare dip continues in #ES_F and good to see after 11 days of upside. 5662 was 1st rally target today and we hit and sold. 5630 561520 were pullback targets. Arriving at 1520 now  We dont sell sustainably until 561520 fails 5587 1st down. 5630 must recover now to pop
